         <div type="translation">
            <p><note>abc</note>: To the emperor Caesar Traianus Hadrianus Augustus <gap reason="lost" unit="character" extent="unknown"/>; 
               <note>d</note>:  . . . ] the gymnasium of the Young Men and the <gap reason="lost" unit="character" extent="unknown"/>; 
               <note>f</note>: . . . ] son of Nikoteimos son of Artemidoros son of Zenon <gap reason="lost" unit="character" extent="unknown"/>; 
               <note>g</note>: . . . ] son of Menandros <gap reason="lost" unit="character" extent="unknown"/></p>
         </div>
